Steps to run the UI in local env;

npm install react-router-dom
npm install recharts


---- GIT COMMANDS to push code to BITBUCKET -----
git branch
git status
git add .
git commit -m "commit changes"
git push origin -u dev/sithu



----- RUN APPLICATION IN LOCAL -----
npm run dev
Open this link in browser >>  http://localhost:3000/



----- DEPLOY COMMANDS -----
git branch (should be in main) 
git remote -v (should show bitbucket as pull origin and github as push origin)
git pull origin main
git push origin main (This will trigger deployment automatically in netlix)

----- Live applicaition -----
https://lerd.netlify.app/login (username - sithu    |    password - 123)



